{
  "video_id": "gv1ApCmctVQ",
  "title": "Sonaar Luthra: Meet the Water Canary",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Cholera was reported in Haiti"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "for the first time in over 50 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "last October."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "There was no way to predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "how far it would spread through water supplies"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "and how bad the situation would get."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "And not knowing where help was needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "always ensured that help was in short supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "in the areas that needed it most."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve gotten good at predicting and preparing for storms"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "before they take innocent lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "and cause irreversible damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "but we still can&#39;t do that with water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s why."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "Right now, if you want to test water in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "you need a trained technician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "expensive equipment like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "and you have to wait about a day"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "for chemical reactions to take place and provide results."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s too slow"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "to get a picture of conditions on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "before they change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "too expensive to implement"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "in all the places that require testing."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "And it ignores the fact that, in the meanwhile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "people still need to drink water."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Most of the information that we collected on the cholera outbreak"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t come from testing water;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "it came from forms like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "which documented all the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "we failed to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "Countless lives have been saved"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "by canaries in coalmines --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "a simple and invaluable way"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "for miners to know whether they&#39;re safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been inspired by that simplicity as I&#39;ve been working on this problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "with some of the most hardworking and brilliant people I&#39;ve ever known."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "We think there&#39;s a simpler solution to this problem --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "one that can be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "by people who face conditions like this everyday."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in its early stages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "but this is what it looks like right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "We call it the Water Canary."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a fast, cheap device"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "that answers an important question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Is this water contaminated?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t require any special training."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "And instead of waiting for chemical reactions to take place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "it uses light."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "That means there&#39;s no waiting"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "for chemical reactions to take place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "no need to use reagents that can run out"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "and no need to be an expert"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "to get actionable information."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "To test water, you simply insert a sample"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "and, within seconds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "it either displays a red light, indicating contaminated water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "or a green light, indicating the sample is safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "This will make it possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "for anyone to collect life-saving information"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "and to monitor water quality conditions as they unfold."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re also, on top of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "integrating wireless networking"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "into an affordable device"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "with GPS and GSM."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "What that means is that each reading can be automatically transmitted to servers"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "to be mapped in real time."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "With enough users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "maps like this will make it possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "to take preventive action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "containing hazards before they turn into emergencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "that take years to recover from."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "And then, instead of taking days"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "to disseminate this information to the people who need it most,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "it can happen automatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen how distributed networks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "big data and information"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "can transform society."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s time for us to apply them to water."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "Our goal over the next year is to get Water Canary ready for the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "and to open-source the hardware"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "so that anyone can contribute to the development and the evaluation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "so we can tackle this problem together."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}